{"tid":343854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[威士忌5] 新手去whiskylive 任飲入門款飲到嘔","createTime":"2017-08-01T20:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T17:19:50.000Z","uid":61267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ab86aa528bf42cf93d5e0ab5b8bb79a780abbc","tid":343854,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T20:15:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">個格式係沿用久米仙巴打開既<br />\n上個post 冇申報番唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔打算自己整一個 會將久米仙巴打 既格式改一改下</span><br />\n<br />\n完全未飲過Whisky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔明有咩咁令人著迷既可以睇下小弟既文章：<br />\n點解唔試下威士忌？ <a href=\"https://is.gd/MsHdou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FMsHdou&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d2a5235e\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/MsHdou</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Basic knowledge基本野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n1. 威士忌達人的威士忌學苑 <a href=\"https://is.gd/OeByyc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FOeByyc&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8c6bb506\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/OeByyc</a><br />\n2. 關於威士忌 書上沒教你的事 <a href=\"https://is.gd/M6C8VQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FM6C8VQ&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2f79981c\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/M6C8VQ</a><br />\n3. Maltmadness Beginners&rsquo;Guide <a href=\"https://is.gd/xouIeM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FxouIeM&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=eae00265\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/xouIeM</a><br />\n4. 關於威士忌不可不知的十件事 <a href=\"https://is.gd/ydAjAs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FydAjAs&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e3769adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/ydAjAs</a><br />\n5. 漫談威士忌品酒技巧 <a href=\"https://is.gd/1O3Fvy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2F1O3Fvy&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f5f8de10\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/1O3Fvy</a><br />\n6. THE MURRAY METHOD <a href=\"http://thewhiskeyscout.com/?page_id=453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthewhiskeyscout.com%2F%3Fpage_id%3D453&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=65b2c330\" target=\"_blank\">http://thewhiskeyscout.com/?page_id=453</a><br />\n7. Whisky Q <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whiskyQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FwhiskyQ%2F&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5a4d8b88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/whiskyQ/</a><br />\n8. 威士忌 從零開始 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/startfromzerotowhisky/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstartfromzerotowhisky%2F&d=TVDa0LtBSmyBeoC%2BwxTZ7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=87c91c90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/startfromzerotowhisky/</a><br />\n小弟<span style=\"color: red;\">(久米仙巴打)</span>開既Page，自己都係新手慢慢學緊，好明白新手係好需要幫助先入到門，就將自己學既野寫出黎比人睇，循序漸進咁一齊學野，亦都會整合人地既資料同文章去比讀者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q and A答問大會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: 新手入門，想識多D又無從入手?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: 個人建議: 一開始唔知自己鍾意飲咩口味既朋友，可以去朋友到痴酒飲下，等朋友Guide住你飲。冇朋友咁點算？可以自己去Ginger(Whisky Bar)試Beginner Set，連埋加一都係132$就試到3杯入門級酒，講緊係8-12年左右既貨色。去酒鋪試酒，好多酒鋪都有開左幾支酒係到比人試，唔洗錢試，如尋麥、威紅、鴻源、億升、the raremalt等。一開始對比唔同風味既酒黎試最好，一杯Sherry風味，一杯泥媒風味，好易就聞到個分別。所以自己買左幾支係屋企飲既朋友，一定要買一對聞香杯，對比自己既酒黎感受個分別。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: 新手入門飲邊隻好?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: 以下係樓主個人推薦，先試多D唔同風味去搵自己岩飲咩味<br />\n花香: TTL Bourbon, Glenmorangie Original, Glenfiddich 12<br />\n雪莉(Sherry): GlenDronach 12, Macallan 12, Balvenie 12 Doublewood<br />\n<br />\n下面就重口味小小，有正露丸，醫院味，煙味同碘酒味，一開始唔建議試<br />\n海風┼煙燻: Talisker 10<br />\n煙燻泥煤: Lagavulin 16, Ardbeg10, Laphroaig 10<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q</span>: Single Malt Whisky同Blended Whisky有咩分別?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>: Single Malt Whisky係指用一間酒廠出產既麥芽威士忌裝入樽既威士忌，並唔係指用同一種麥芽製成既威士忌，代表之一: Macallan 12。Blended Whisky係用唔同酒廠出產既威士忌調合而成，而用於調合既威士忌原材料可以係唔同穀物，如大麥(barley)、裸麥(rye)、小麥(wheat)、玉米(corn)。代表之一: Johnnie Walker"},{"pid":"e09f037957b674bf320b7cd8bda5cc6db2424dd1","tid":343854,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:57:37.000Z","msg":"新post 輕輕一推"},{"pid":"16807c9b35e4709e04ba3f63e71ed21eaf9a18b3","tid":343854,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"朋友話bowmore 12唔啱飲，唔鐘意個味係咪唔洗試laga 16<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"b0185d61fb58ebe1aac45ff687517af463eec749","tid":343854,"uid":17705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"啱先喺東京買左支talisker18 , 11800"}]}